但當你一唔留神，佢隨時會出現吞噬你。呢隻巨獸叫做情緒。<br />\n<br />\n要對付情緒巨獸，我哋可以選擇去面對佢。另外，如果你覺得已經冇力反抗，隨時會俾負面情緒打敗嘅話，記得要搵幫手。而我哋OPEN噏就有豐富情緒支援經驗，幫你對付巨獸。<br />\n<br />\nOpen噏網上情緒支援服務： <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=raogrMnRIgwaKnbVZhVJo%2FUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=83937f74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a> / SMS: 91 012 012 / FB Messenger: <a href=\"http://m.me/hkopenup\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.me%2Fhkopenup&d=raogrMnRIgwaKnbVZhVJo%2FUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=3ee34447\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">m.me/hkopenup</a> / WeChat: hkopenup <br />\n<br />\n#Open噏  #OpenUp  #hkopenup #24小時同你一齊分擔 #MessageUs #緊急情緒支援平台 #Messenger #哥斯拉<br />\n======================== <br />\n想知道更多我哋嘅消息？可以讚好我哋專頁！"},{"pid":"1f0bdaa08a9a25674636e315b37f30d224c68302","tid":1266110,"uid":126005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c468f5f863390ff6bab16e5a67ad200743e3f767","tid":1266110,"uid":233905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":18,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T12:54:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T14:15:56.000Z","msg":"Me2。但不要死啊"},{"pid":"3e2ef884f04592e8852c941bf24d28f303dd194d","tid":1266110,"uid":6111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T14:16:08.000Z","msg":"咁樣自殺叫死得有價值咩？"},{"pid":"7deec6cb8122663b4a7871fdf562d42fbcc738fc","tid":1266110,"uid":37723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T14:16:29.000Z","msg":"留低條命 第日先做到更大貢獻 <br />\n一日未死 一日未輸"},{"pid":"f5fb953e600c0d86fa82ec541f61edf5fd4da3b1","tid":1266110,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T14:16:34.000Z","msg":"求下你唔好呀！我地仲再需要你架！！！<br />\n無論幾困難都一齊行落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62fc465ee9ab6731a4189615f04c7e35c46e24ee","tid":1266110,"uid":209198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":